    "The closeness also depends on the sensitivity of the optimal values (P ⋆ p, P ⋆) to the constraints via the optimal dual variables (λ ⋆ ν, λ ⋆ p).",
    "Thus, it captures the optimality of the parametrized dual value D ⋆ p. Hence, the multi-shot constrained alignment of Algorithm 1 approximately solves Problem (P-CA).",
